body:
**JavaScript support directly on the server for your Minecraft events.**
## 🎉 JavaScript right in Minecraft!
A highly flexible mod for script-based events.

![Test Script](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/7e37cd0df03d6e5cf9f26a181b9b1e420694b689.gif)

## ✨ A handy JS editor!
Coding directly in Minecraft.
![Editor JS](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/456e69a9727e942f5ab7d48968b3ed6395f52f19.png)

### Simple code:

```
// Trigger an event when a player joins the server
Events.onJoin(playerName => {
    // Send a "Hello World!" title to the player's screen
    Player.sendTitle(playerName, "Hello World!", "", 10, 70, 20);
});
```

**ScriptAPI** documentation is available [here](https://github.com/TheTimStage/JsScripts/blob/main/README.md).

Thanks to **Froska729** for creating the mod icons!❤️
